<div>
    <div class="code-block">
        <button class="copy-button" data-clipboard-target="#curl-initiate-code">
            <i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
        </button>
        <pre><code class="language-bash" id="curl-initiate-code">curl -X POST https://checkout.cachetechs.com/api/initiatePaymentIntent \
